@startuml
title 2.18.2.4 Notification Preferences

skinparam maxMessageSize 250
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #ffffff
    ActorBackgroundColor #ffffff
}

autonumber

actor ":User" as U
participant ":NotificationPreferencesPage" as Client
participant ":NotificationController" as Ctrl
participant ":NotificationService" as Svc
participant ":NotificationRepository" as Repo
participant ":Database" as DB

activate U

' === Get Preferences ===
U ->> Client : Open notification preferences page

Client ->> Ctrl : GET /api/notifications/preferences
activate Ctrl

Ctrl ->> Ctrl : ExtractUserContext() from JWT claims
Ctrl ->> Svc : GetPreferencesAsync(userId, ct)
activate Svc

Svc ->> Repo : GetPreferencesAsync(userId, ct)
activate Repo

Repo ->> DB : Query all notification preferences\nfor this user, ordered by type
activate DB
DB -->> Repo : Return list of persisted preferences
deactivate DB

Repo -->> Svc : List<NotificationPreference>
deactivate Repo

Svc ->> Svc : Merge persisted preferences with\nall NotificationType enum values;\ndefault IsEnabled=true, SoundEnabled=true\nfor types without a saved preference

Svc -->> Ctrl : List<NotificationPreferenceDto>
deactivate Svc

Ctrl -->> Client : 200 OK - ApiResponse<List<NotificationPreferenceDto>>
deactivate Ctrl

Client -->> U : Display preference toggles\nfor each notification type

' === Update Preferences ===
U ->> Client : Toggle preferences and click Save

Client ->> Ctrl : PUT /api/notifications/preferences\nBody: UpdateNotificationPreferencesRequest
activate Ctrl

Ctrl ->> Ctrl : ExtractUserContext() from JWT claims
Ctrl ->> Svc : UpdatePreferencesAsync(userId, request, ct)
activate Svc

Svc ->> Svc : Map NotificationPreferenceItemRequest list\nto NotificationPreference entities

Svc ->> Repo : UpsertPreferencesAsync(userId, preferences, ct)
activate Repo

Repo ->> DB : Fetch existing preferences for this user
activate DB
DB -->> Repo : Return existing preference records
deactivate DB

Repo ->> Repo : For each preference in request:\n- If exists: update IsEnabled, SoundEnabled, UpdatedAt\n- If new: insert new record

Repo ->> DB : Save all changes (update existing + insert new)
activate DB
DB -->> Repo : Confirm save
deactivate DB

Repo -->> Svc : Completed
deactivate Repo

Svc -->> Ctrl : Completed
deactivate Svc

Ctrl -->> Client : 200 OK - "Notification preferences updated."
deactivate Ctrl

Client -->> U : Display success confirmation

deactivate U

@enduml
